{"reponsecode":0,"reponsemessage":"","data":{"exhibit_id":"scsbwy_gshz_qtzmmj","exhibition_name":"古蜀华章","location":"502,363","name":"纵目青铜面像","size":"","like":1,"share_url":"mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=3582","share_url2":"https://share.morview.com/#/share?id=scsbwy_gshz_qtzmmj","is_favorited":0,"_3d_url":"museum/show3d.php?fileroot=scbwy_museum&exhibit_id=3582&scale=2","description":"这件硕大的青铜面像是三星堆文化最具标识特征的器物之一。面像呈方脸、宽颐（yí）、臣字形眼，脸型与同时出土的其他人面像或头像相近，但双耳巨大、瞳孔纵出，显然是古蜀人在人面像基础上所做的艺术升华，是蜀人精神世界的写照。|据《华阳国志·蜀志》记载，蜀人的先王蚕丛“其目纵，始称王”。三星堆的这件纵目面像，应当是古蜀人对先王传说的朦胧记忆，是古蜀人用以祭拜或供奉的神像。|年代：商|尺寸：高 66 厘米，宽 138 厘米，厚 85 厘米|来源：1980 年广汉三星堆遗址二号坑出土，三星堆博物馆藏","images":["content/fileroot/museum/scbwy_museum/image/SiNazrz1k_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/scbwy_museum/image/SiNazrz1k1_s.webp","content/fileroot/museum/scbwy_museum/image/SiNazrz1k2_s.webp"],"audio":[{"audiotype":"mandarin","filename":"content/fileroot/museum/scbwy_museum/audio/6JqVadxFKf.mp3"}],"video":{"videourl":"","img":""},"ispaid":1}}